headline.print_headline: No Charges for Wrestlers in Lynching Photo
headline.main: No Charges for Wrestlers in Lynching Photo

lead_paragraph: A New Jersey prosecutor says no charges will be filed against the members of a high school wrestling team who posed in a photograph that simulated a lynching.
